Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:24:00.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:24:00.33,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}願那讓你苦不堪言的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:05.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:05.66,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}會迎來完結的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:09.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:09.46,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}而我卻要目送你離開
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:12.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:12.75,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我們終將會重來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.88,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}重來對新一天的期待
